stateDiagram
  [*] --> UnderBudget
  UnderBudget --> Warning: provider-billed usage reaches threshold
  Warning --> UnderBudget: reset period or budget increased
  Warning --> Exceeded: provider-billed budget crossed
  Exceeded --> Acknowledged: user dismisses alert
  Acknowledged --> Exceeded: latest sync still above budget
  Exceeded --> UnderBudget: reset period / clear budget
